-)what is themeDisplay?
ThemeDisplay is a utility object that provide all the information about the current portal context 
including logged in user ,site,page,company and theme details.

site(Group)
Page(Layout)
portalURL-Domain of the Portal.
themeDisplay.isSignedIn= return false if user is not logged in 
                         return true if user id logged in 

-)what is Client Extension?
A client Extestion is used for extension the Liferay's Functionality without modifying it's core code
it's promote loose coupling by keeping customization independent from the main system .


